## Laundry in Kashmir — local context

Kashmir's seasons affect what goes into the laundry basket. Heavy winter clothing, wool layers, and traditional garments need careful washing or dry cleaning rather than harsh home cycles. Formal events — weddings, Eid gatherings, university functions — create spikes in demand for pressed, stain-free outfits on short notice.

When you book through Panun Kaergar, you are using a service designed for Srinagar households. Partners understand local garment types and can advise on dry clean versus wash for delicate fabrics. You can list items when booking — number of pieces, fabric type, stains to treat — so the partner arrives or schedules pickup with the right expectations.

For families who prefer not to carry heavy laundry bags across town, pickup and delivery options (where available) save time and hassle. Panun Kaergar's review system helps the community identify laundry partners who consistently deliver quality care across Srinagar.

