## Tips before your laundry pickup or visit in Srinagar

A little preparation helps your order go smoothly and protects your garments:

- **Separate delicate items** — sarees, wool, silk — and note them in your booking.
- **Point out stains** when handing over clothes so they can be pre-treated.
- **Empty pockets** and remove belts or accessories from trousers and coats.
- **Count pieces** when booking bulk laundry so pricing and turnaround are accurate.
- **Be home or have someone available** for pickup and delivery windows.

For wedding or event outfits, book a few days ahead when possible to allow proper dry cleaning and pressing. If you need express service, mention the deadline when you call or WhatsApp so we can match you with an available partner.

